essage, we should have each bullet followed by a blank line, and then after the last bullet we also need a blank line? The rule says: \"Every Telegram message. No exceptions.\" and \"After every bullet, every item, every section → blank line.\" So after each bullet we need a blank line. That means our message should look like:\n\n• We set up the workspace...\n\n[blank line]\n• I read SOUL.md...\n\n[blank line]\n• I read USER.md...\n\n[blank line]\n• I checked MEMORY.md...\n\n[blank line]\n• I said hello...\n\n[blank line]\n\nAnd then maybe we can have a final bullet for the question? Or we can end with a blank line after the last bullet. The section end also needs a blank line. So we'll have a blank line after the last bullet.\n\nLet's craft the message accordingly.\n\nWe'll send via message tool and then output NO_REPLY.\n\nLet's do it.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c8f59afef03b442c935dcab1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"• We set up the workspace with .md file structure and Notion integration.\n\n• I read SOUL.md to remember who I am (bbymama, friendly assistant).\n\n• I read USER.md to understand your background and goals.\n\n• I checked MEMORY.md for our long-term context (workspace setup, Notion integration).\n\n• I said hello and asked how I can help.\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":20093,"output":1203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21296,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774822075844,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a9e77b7fd3042952"}}
